{"tid":1925782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖）有冇手足畀佢呃過錢？","createTime":"2020-03-14T15:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T16:29:36.000Z","uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"758fc29fdc531090d2fcc995c56ac5e06bd1e423","tid":1925782,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"前樓豬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iU4A1Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiU4A1Qe.jpg&h=196a996b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0A6jJ3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0A6jJ3z.jpg&h=74a8033c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VCiZBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VCiZBV.jpg&h=efd49d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條撚樣之前借香港而家發生緊嘅事嚟扮可憐話跳樓<br />\n之後到最後俾人發現佢成日話跳樓都係搏可憐<br />\n之後就好多手足關心佢 佢就借題發揮成日話自己無錢/病左/交電話費嚟呃手足錢 仲要呃人感情呃埋男朋友啲錢（唔好歧視同性戀）<br />\n佢8月份個陣試過一腳踏7-8船全部無見過因為佢淨係貪啲會俾錢佢既人<br />\n佢成日都問佢啲網友（借）錢<br />\n～完～<br />\n純粹想問下有冇手足/其他人俾佢呃過錢"},{"pid":"f918366d4dbeb10c8333a123714921cc56d3974c","tid":1925782,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZajXKOC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZajXKOC.png&h=ce01e39c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea371bd7466002dc69ccce83c2291cfdd7028102","tid":1925782,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"今次唔好又自爆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6596dfe47b42ed8dd89b0957a4946ea841ef7cf2","tid":1925782,"uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Nru1r12.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNru1r12.png&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCQ9axkDo